abstract: >
  Code, data, and analysis package for the study of self-referential consistency
  in stateless large language models, including matched temperature comparisons,
  automated behavioral metrics, anonymized human-evaluation materials, and
  figure-generation scripts.

keywords:
  - large language models
  - self-reference
  - pseudo-consciousness
  - behavioral evaluation
  - natural language inference
  - human evaluation
  - reproducibility

